      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «أَسَاسُ اَلْبَيْتِ مِنَ اَلْأَرْضِ اَلسَّابِعَةِ اَلسُّفْلَى إِلَى اَلْأَرْضِ اَلسَّابِعَةِ اَلْعُلْيَا»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2317 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"The foundation of the House (Kaaba) extends from the seventh layer of the lower earth to the seventh layer of the upper earth.\""
        ]
      }
